rows.label: tlk43310148_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Go down that stairway and it'll
take you to Fons Maim Port.

rows.label: tlk43310148_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Sometimes the Divine Beast dives into
the sea. When it does, you can't open
the doors. So, you can't leave.

rows.label: tlk43310148_03_msg0003
rows.name:
But, luckily, that's not the
case right now. So we can
come and go as we please.

rows.label: tlk43310148_03_msg0004
rows.name:
You could take a boat over to
another Divine Beast, no bother.

rows.label: tlk43310148_03_msg0005
rows.name:
'Course, you've no hope of going
direct to Superbia. We cut ties with
'em when it all kicked off, see.
